FrieslandCampina WAMCO Nigeria Plc, producers of Peak and Three Crowns milk, has unveiled WAMCO Academy, a world class training centre, as part of the company’s efforts to promote its business and employees’ growth. During the inauguration, the President, Consumer Dairy, Royal FrieslandCampina, The Netherlands, Roel Van Neerbos, emphasised the need to ‘turn talents into top performers’ which he said the academy would help to achieve. The Managing Director, FrieslandCampina WAMCO, Mr. Ben Langat, explained some of the features that make the new facility technically outstanding. “Our new training academy is purpose built and equipped to enhance the skills of our employees who deliver some of the best global practices that FrieslandCampina WAMCO is known for across Nigeria,” he said.